it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.objects

Class AbstractObject2DoubleMap.BasicEntry<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.objects.AbstractObject2DoubleMap.BasicEntry<K>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Object2DoubleMap.Entry<K>, java.util.Map.Entry<K,java.lang.Double>
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractObject2DoubleMap<K>

    public static class AbstractObject2DoubleMap.BasicEntry<K>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Object2DoubleMap.Entry<K>
    This class provides a basic but complete type-specific entry class for all those maps implementations that do not have entries on their own (e.g., most immutable maps).

    This class does not implement setValue(), as the modification would not be reflected in the base map.
